chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888df11fad1ffcc2879cda36d3a335a0189e0156","tid":156620,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"搞錯，乜唔係免費咩？"},{"pid":"0e769d58a3c6b106b67b3d4616f172c1368f3efb","tid":156620,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那一早當香港外人<br />\n支那廿年<br />\n香港玩完</blockquote><br />\n外國買野係貴d既"},{"pid":"3409394e68c14b3b672c5fe606640c6bef9b0bde","tid":156620,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搞錯，乜唔係免費咩？</blockquote><br />\n免費比我飲垃圾水 不了"},{"pid":"5fbb1cd909045de46f0bbf3c398ab296e95badc8","tid":156620,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"🇨🇳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa1767c332813d1bbe7c83ac6740d771834f3e0","tid":156620,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:46:19.000Z","msg":"飲水思源<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起D屍水都想嘔<br />\n仲要焗買"},{"pid":"7282f119401087604b48839e15b87b29fa5126e0","tid":156620,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母支那狗<br />\n<br />\n成撚日話東江水上遊為咗香港唔開發<br />\n<br />\n啲水你淨係賣俾香港咩？<br />\n<br />\n深圳咪又係幫你買梗，有本事唔撚賣俾深圳，只俾香港丫。"},{"pid":"d0424a15a49773a7183b3cc7fc7070a8d2ad8a36","tid":156620,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"乜唔係深圳就快有錢過香港咩<br />\n<br />\n深圳人咁撚有錢 點解可以買平水 我地咁撚窮要買貴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b92ce2c235d00689f1a649ff5ce4587530bd7c","tid":156620,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多年夾埋啲錢夠起幾多淨化廠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前quote過起化淡廠大約要200億<br />\n<br />\n其實只係4年買水既錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a72a74452bcaea0723b4ac3ae86a8e41bd61b70","tid":156620,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T21:23:42.000Z","msg":"飲水思原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一諗就燥啦你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8645ccd369698c238ada8c950d8d633c4474ebe9","tid":156620,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T22:35:09.000Z","msg":"Jr 啦"},{"pid":"0db2676c08ca6191da445ccc1d44a4d146b21a71","tid":156620,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:00:15.000Z","msg":"大家心知肚明啦， 撳住搶<br />\n乜都貴過人， 仲迫你買<br />\n基建全部超支不斷<br />\n當香港提款機"},{"pid":"f0a4cf8665413e9920baec10c322f4b87f8d11db","tid":156620,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T03:10:45.000Z","msg":"有蔣麗云呢啲八婆響香港做立委、有投呢啲人做議員嘅盲毛，就唔怪得支那賣我地能量水，一個願打一個願捱，抵撚做傻仔!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f6aedf89adc5737a3034467c7ee1adbda85630","tid":156620,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁多年夾埋啲錢夠起幾多淨化廠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前quote過起化淡廠大約要200億<br />\n<br />\n其實只係4年買水既錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實海水化淡最大問題唔係建做成本，而係現有技術好難將海水入面既重金屬完全去除，入黎沖涼淋花ok但係長期飲用好易有問題<br />\n<br />\n同埋海水化淡又會做成污染，到時d環保撚又會出黎阻頭阻勢<br />\n<br />\n所以建議係東南亞買水好過"},{"pid":"49e07f6f9af18357ad1738990eba097514d52b0d","tid":156620,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T23:06:42.000Z","msg":"真心想知，如果香港唔比錢買水<br />\n大陸可以點做？"}]}